<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.9">
<l>viḷampu māṟucamaya mumavai yākiyu maṟṟuntaṉpā</l>
<l>laḷantu kāṇṭaṟkariya ṉākiya vātippi rāṉamarum</l>
<l>vaḷaṅko ṭaṇpaṇaicūḻntaḻa kāya tirukkuru kūrataṉai</l>
<l>yuḷaṅkoṇ ñāṉattuvaimmi ṉummai yuyyakkoṇṭu pōkuṟilē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking into [your] minds</l>
<l>Tirukkurukūr that is beautiful, being surrounded by fertile cool fields</l>
<l>where abides the primeval lord who is difficult to measure [and] see</l>
<l>on the part of the six doctrines that are proclaimed, although they are those, and [any] other,</l>
	<l>put knowledge [there], if you undertake to go, [he] taking you so that you escape.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
